cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.CY. 

This paper deals with natural language processing and machine learning techniques to detect insincere questions in social media. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). Additionally, the use of machine learning models such as SVM, Naive Bayes, GRU, and LSTM suggests that the paper could also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also involves text classification and information retrieval, which could place it in cs.IR (Information Retrieval) and cs.CY (Computers and Society).
